OL,3,CHospital staff to wear body cameras
OL,4,Cafter increase in violence
OL,6,FStaff at Gloucestershire Royal
OL,7,FHospital's Emergency Department have
OL,8,Fbegun wearing body-worn cameras after
OL,9,Fan increase in abusive and aggressive
OL,10,Fbehaviour.
OL,12,FThe 12-week trial started on 10 April
OL,13,Fin a bid to increase security and
OL,14,Fsafety for patients, staff and the
OL,15,Fpublic.
