OL,6,FA spokesperson from Gloucestershire
OL,7,FHospitals NHS Foundation Trust said:
OL,8,F"We are taking this step to support
OL,9,Fthe de-escalation of incidents and
OL,10,Fsupport action that is taken following
OL,11,Fsafety incidents in terms of
OL,12,Fidentifying and prosecuting any
OL,13,Foffenders.
