OL,3,CHospital staff to wear body cameras
OL,4,Cafter increase in violence
OL,6,F"The cameras will be worn by key staff
OL,7,Fin the Emergency Department and also
OL,8,Fby the Gloucestershire Royal Hospital
OL,9,Fsecurity response team who may respond
OL,10,Fto other departments in the hospital
OL,11,Fbut will only be activated during an
OL,12,Fincident of abuse, violence,
OL,13,Faggression or security risk."
OL,15,FIndividuals who are being aggressive
OL,16,For violent will be informed that the
OL,17,Fcamera is recording and the body
OL,18,Fcameras will not be switched on during
OL,19,Fnormal clinical activities.
